com.tokelon.toktales.core.render.order

Interface IRenderLayerStack.IStackNavigator

  • Enclosing interface:
    IRenderLayerStack

    public static interface IRenderLayerStack.IStackNavigator
    Can be used to navigate through the positions of a stack.

    All navigation positions return whether the current position is valid or not.
